column2: Nano Monster Truck Playset
column3:
Get excited with this Trendtimes Nano Monster Power Launchers 12-Piece Monster Truck Playset. This playset comes with 2 different colored Nano Monster Trucks, 2 Power Key Launchers as well as 2 barrels, 2 traffic cones, 2 street signs, 1 street light, 1 ramp and 1 ring of fire. Insert the Power Key Launcher into the back of any Nano Monster and press the button on the Power Key to launch them at incredible speeds. You can set up the playset pieces however you'd like and launch these monster trucks through the awesome ring of fire. Durable polymer construction gives these Nano Monsters the ability to take hard hits and keep on racing. At an inch and a quarter tall take these little monsters with you anywhere. Get your Trendtimes Nano Monster Power Launchers 12-Piece Monster Truck Playset and start launching these awesome monster trucks today!

Features:

  • Durable Polymer Construction
  • High Speed Launching Action
  • 12-Piece Playset
  • Ages 3+
  • Quick and Easy Set Up

Includes:

  • Trendtimes Nano Monster Power Launchers 12-Piece Monster Truck Playset

column2: Goblin Racing Drone RC Quadcopter
column3:
Speed through the skies at an amazing 25 MPH with the newest drone from Trendtimes Elite, the Elite Goblin 2.4GHz 4.5CH 25 MPH RC Racing Drone!

This awesome racing drone features a lightweight body constructed of durable polymer to handle rough conditions and hard landings. It boasts 4.5 channel controls meaning you can fly up/down, forward/backward, strafe left/right and rotate left/right. The the .5 in the channel indicates that it contains an internal gyro that helps you to always have a smooth flight even at the top speed of 25 MPH. Show your impressive skills rolling and flipping in the air with the flip stunt mode. It comes with a 2.4GHz transmitter, so radio interference won't be a problem even with other mini drones in the area. Hurry and get the Trendtimes Elite Goblin 25 MPH Racing Drone today!

column2: Amazing Creatures Frog Synthetic Dissection Kit - STEM
column3:
Ignite your child's curiosity and love of learning with the Amazing Creatures Frog Synthetic Dissection Kit! This dissection kit allows kids to learn animal anatomy without the risk of sharp objects or unsanitary specimens. With an easy-to-cut gel body and anatomically accurate bones and organs, kids can learn the internal anatomy of the Frog without the mess and danger of real dissections. Using the included safe surgical instruments, and following along with the included instruction manual, they will learn the placement and function of each major organ. Comes with refill packets and a reusable mold, allowing your child to enjoy the kit again and again. Learning and fun come together with the Amazing Creatures Frog Synthetic Dissection Kit!

  • Learn Animal Anatomy With Safe And Sanitary Equipment

  • Refills Included, Allowing Multiple Dissections

column2: Silverlit V-Beat Air Guitar
column3:
Rock out to your favorite tracks with V-Beat Air Guitar! Whether you want to strum your heart out like a musically challenged pop group or throw yourself body, soul and air guitar into a rocking Led Zeppelin guitar solo, we've found the perfect platform to launch your musical dream in the tidy package V-Beat Air Guitar. V-Beat Air Guitar gives all wannabe pop and rock stars a dummies guide to rocking on, with a miniature guitar you can't fail to get the hang of. The body and neck of your air guitar are broken into two separate pieces like your very own authentically smashed up guitar of rock legends. Move the neck closer or further away from the body to adjust pitch and use the pick to strum ultra sonic sensors for major, minor and 7th chords. Easy! Play with background melodies or improvise with your own music jam. You can even plug in your MP3 player to the small base unit and rock out to your favorite tracks. Rock and roll!
